{
  "texts": [
    "Humans always use a variety of modalities to portray emotions during interactions.",
    "Researchers classified human modalities into audiovisual (facial expression, voice, gesture, posture, etc.)",
    "and physiological (respiration, skin temperature, etc.)",
    "[159].The general methods for recognizing a person's emotion are speech, facial expression, or gesture.",
    "The speech signal can determine the emotional state of the speaker [159]."
  ]
}